Ethereal.help: You can Phase Shift to become out of sync with normal space. Although you do not become completely Invisible, you are translucent and hard to see. You are intangible, and cannot be affected by those in normal space.

Petrifying_Gaze.help: The Petrifying Gaze has stopped you in your tracks!

Dark_Obliteration.help: You hurl a large blast of negative energy that violently explodes on impact, exposing the dark power of the Netherworld to all foes near the target. Dark Obliteration can reduce the Accuracy of all affected targets. You must have Gloom or Soul Tentacles before selecting this power. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Slow

Shadow_Fall.help: Envelops you and your nearby teammates in a shroud of darkness. Shadow Fall does not grant Invisibility, but it does make you harder to detect. Even if you are discovered, Shadow Fall grants a bonus to Defense bonus to all attacks and Resistance to Fear, while reducing Energy, Negative Energy, and Psionic Damage. You cannot use any other Concealment type power while using Shadow Fall. Recharge: Slow
Shadow_Fall.shortHelp: Toggle: PBAoE, Team Stealth, +DEF(All), +Res(Energy, Negative, Psionics, Fear)
Shadow_Fall.targetHelp: Shadow Fall has made you difficult to detect, which increases your Defense. Shadowfall also partially absorbs and deflects Energy, Negative Energy and Psionic damage. You are also less fearful.
Shadow_Fall.victimHit: You are hidden within the Shadow Fall.

Twilight_Grasp.help: The Twilight Grasp has reduced your Accuracy and Damage potential.

Dark_Regeneration.help: You can tap the dark essence of the Netherworld to drain a small amount of life from all enemies nearby, thus healing yourself. The more foes affected, the more you will be healed. Damage: Minor, Recharge: Slow
